description: Scandinavian Biogas Fuels International AB engages in designing and operating biogas plants. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 92 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-12-16. Th Company sells renewable energy based on compressed biogas (CBG) and liquid biogas (LBG), as well as several related services and is engaged in expertise in the design and operation of biogas facilities with the purpose to optimise biogas and bio-fertiliser production. The Company’s main products are biogas used in heat production, upgraded and liquid biogas used as vehicle fuel, and bio-fertiliser as a substitute for artificial fertiliser. Scandinavian Biogas Fuels International AB operates primarily in the Nordic Region and South Korea.
